            "heading": "INNOVATIVE",
            "text": "<p>We don’t follow categories, we create them. As the first of its kind, our Deodorant Enhancer®️ redefines what it means to stay fresh by working <em>with</em> your deodorant, not replacing it. It’s a new approach, built from the ground up to solve a problem no one else was addressing...and that’s just the beginning.</p>"
