    "founder": {
      "type": "image-text-block",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "",
        "heading": "Meet Our Founders",
        "body": "<p>Our brand was born from a simple but overlooked truth: deodorant alone just doesn’t work.</p><p>We know this because we experienced it ourselves. For years we kept asking the same question so many people quietly wonder: Why doesn’t my deodorant work? We tried everything - natural deodorants, clinical formulas, switching brands, home remedies, armpit masks. Yet, the problem did not go away. It was frustrating, embarrassing, and oddly never talked about openly.</p><p>Odor is universal, emotionally loaded, and scientifically misunderstood. Most deodorants simply mask smell, leaving the real culprit untouched: the odor-causing bacteria that break down sweat and create odor molecules. The category had been stuck solving the symptom, not the source. That’s when we had a moment of clarity: If this problem affects so many people, why hasn’t anyone solved it properly and effectively? So we decided we would.</p><p>Together we (Diana + Alexandra - Mom/Daughter Duo) developed the Deodorant Enhancer®️. A completely new product category. The world’s first patented intricately engineered spray designed to address odor at the source by optimizing the underarm microbiome. Instead of replacing deodorant BAUDIE works with it, creating an environment where deodorant can perform better, longer, and more consistently.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/5B9301A1-5F5C-422F-BF4B-72EA47568F7E.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_aspect_ratio": "portrait",
        "container_width": "full",
